title: Pulse Gossip: Oops: Victoria Kimani dips booty in mud
text:
By Pulse team Sunday, Oct 25th 2015 at 10:32 Victoria Kimani Photo: courtesy 
You know her for pushing buttons but now it’s bums she’s pushing; her booty is in the mud...literally. 
After releasing a teaser of her soon-to-be-released video Booty Bounce, critics now think Victoria Kimani is borrowing a bit too much from Nicki Minaj’s Anaconda. But, well, that’s not our opinion. 
In the teaser, the sassy singing beauty ‘wiggle wiggles’ her money-maker in the mud wearing her bikini...and there is no doubt, this one will cause a storm. 
Sources tell Pulse the video will be out next week. SIMILAR STORIES
